<title>Immanuel Gamnuom !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khen lohna gam ka ngai ie;
 Immanuel gam nuom;
 Lungtuok gibang khennang lenkawl ah ni a suok,
 Ka ngai khenlohna Zion tang hawih chu.

[V2]
 Ka ngai ie van khaw tuol nuom,
 Gi bang khenlohna mun;
 Ka Lal mel leh hinna tuolthing;
 Saron pak hawih a lun.

[V3]
 2. Van Jerusalem hawih ah,
 Hinna damtui a luong;
 Mita muhlouh gam leh hinna tuolthing lim nuoi,
 Salem tuolnuom ah nau bang ei pui in.

[V4]
 3. Lalna gam khawpi achun,
 Van Belam No A leng;
 Zan thim lungngaihna leh nau bang kahna umlo,
 Zing dawng sawl No vakna gam ninnuom ah.

[V5]
 4. Lalna khawpi chanchin chu,
 Gensen guol ahi puoi;
 Lal Hukdampa leh serafim zaila sakna,
 Lal tuollenna Zion tang lopi chu.</lyrics>
</song>